dct_title_s: Delaware River Billingsport to Fort Mifflin
dct_description_sm: Map extends from Lincoln Park to North Mantua along the Delaware River.

Map shows proposed cut-off channel at Mouth of Mantua Creek from a survey made under the direction of Lieutenant Colonel C. W. Raymond. Map also shows suggested Riparian line through Mantua Creek as well as river front and property of Albertson & Parry.
